==Spanish==
===Etymology===
Latin ''[[pensare]]''
===Verb===
[[Category:Spanish verbs]]
'''pensar'''
# to [[think]]
# to [[reflect]] upon a situation
# to [[intend]]; to [[try]]

===Usage===
*I think therefore I am - ''Pienso luego soy''
*Do you think that history is good? - ''Piensas que la historia es buena?'' (Could also use [[creer]])

